About Us
About Us
Who We Are
Throughout the 90's and early 2000's, the restaurant was previously known as "The Great Outdoors Caf√©" and was a local favorite. It closed thereafter and remained closed for several years. After changing ownership it reopened as "The Great Outdoors Restaurant" with the goal of providing excellent food & drink, and being a gathering place for all. Since 2008 we have remained true to that goal. Providing tasty options for everyone, friendly service, and indoor and outdoor dining options, we invite you to become part of the story.
Led by Leadership
General Manager Anthony Paparella
Eat. Drink. Relax.
We proudly feature live music every Wednesday, Friday, Saturday, and Sunday Evenings. From local favorites to talented up-and-coming artists. For event listings, please visit our FB page or click on the button below.

photoswipe markup
Root element of PhotoSwipe. Must have class pswp.
Background of PhotoSwipe. 
         It's a separate element as animating opacity is faster than rgba().
Slides wrapper with overflow:hidden.
Container that holds slides. 
            PhotoSwipe keeps only 3 of them in the DOM to save memory.
            Don't modify these 3 pswp__item elements, data is added later on.
Default (PhotoSwipeUI_Default) interface on top of sliding area. Can be changed.
Controls are self-explanatory. Order can be changed.
